; 20260428  v2.1  Adjusted reactive behaviors to use variables defined in proactive file (Mohammed)
; 20260428  v2.1  Implemented reactive actions (like, share, ignore, report, reply) (Hamed)
; 20260428  v2.1  Connected reactive actions to selectedAction variable (Hamed)
; 20260428  v2.2  Ensured only one action executed per step (subsumption logic) (Hamed)
; 20260511  v2.3  Added reactive communication actions for human agents: (Hamed)
; 20260511  v2.3  accept/reject bot requests and inform-agency messaging (Hamed)
; 20260511  v2.3  using ACL-style performatives. (Hamed)
